description: Provides sending statistics for the current Amazon Web Services Region. The result is a list of data points, representing the last two weeks of sending activity. Each data point in the list contains statistics for a 15-minute period of time. You can execute this operation no more than once per second.

nested_items.name: SendDataPoints
nested_items.description: A list of data points, each of which represents 15 minutes of activity.

nested_items.name: DeliveryAttempts
nested_items.description: Number of emails that have been sent.

nested_items.name: Bounces
nested_items.description: Number of emails that have bounced.

nested_items.name: Complaints
nested_items.description: Number of unwanted emails that were rejected by recipients.

nested_items.name: Rejects
nested_items.description: Number of emails rejected by Amazon SES.
